bundle.name: Qlik Dashboard bundle
bundle.description:
This is a set of supported extensions that will facilitate dashboard creation in Qlik Sense: A navigation button, a date picker, a slider, and two different container objects. These can be used in addition to the native objects found under "Charts".

For limitations and support conditions, see the documentation.
